You are finally awake.

10
00:00:46,660 --> 00:00:48,540
I was just messing with you.

11
00:00:48,540 --> 00:00:49,860
You actually believed it.

12
00:00:49,860 --> 00:00:52,020
It was so funny.

13
00:00:56,140 --> 00:00:57,140
I'm okay.

14
